Logic Builder (FizzBuzz)
 Code:
def fizz_buzz():
    fizz = 0
    buzz = 0
    fizzbuzz = 0

    for i in range(1, 51):
        if i % 3 == 0 and i % 5 == 0:
            print("FizzBuzz")
            fizzbuzz += 1
        elif i % 3 == 0:
            print("Fizz")
            fizz += 1
        elif i % 5 == 0:
            print("Buzz")
            buzz += 1
        else:
            print(i)

    print("\n--- Count ---")
    print("Fizz:", fizz)
    print("Buzz:", buzz)
    print("FizzBuzz:", fizzbuzz)

fizz_buzz()
 Explanation
Uses loop from 1 to 50
Checks divisibility using %
